Name: White Haven Mysteries
About the game: Imagine waking up, with no idea who you are, in an abandoned building. You have been drugged by a man who taunts you with his experiments, haunting your every step. A nail biting Hidden Object thriller, explore eerie scenes all while testing your wits. It’s up to you to find the antidote, before it’s too late…and unravel the mystery of White Haven. FEATURES: • Explore Chilling Scenes • A Nail Biting Adventure • Mind Bending Puzzles • Twisted Storyline • Unique Horror experience
